modShortDescription: Tired of using vanilla blocks to simulate every day items? This 7 Days to Die mod adds 22 sorely needed commercial kitchen, bathroom and sales floor blocks.
modDescription:
Tired of using vanilla blocks to simulate every day items? This may help! Adds kitchen, bathroom and sales floor commercial blocks. This 7 Days to Die mod adds 22 sorely needed commercial kitchen, bathroom and sales floor blocks.

[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Commercial_Blocks)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/), Chiko
